                    </div>


                    <div class="col-sm-4 col-md-4 col-lg-4">
                        <div class="">
                            <div class="dark-area clearfix">
                                <div class="c100 p100 dark">
                                    <span>3.7M</span>
                                    <div class="slice">
                                        <div class="bar"></div>
                                        <div class="fill"></div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="text" style="font-weight:bold">3.7 million more people read letterbox media than a daily newspaper Monday to Friday.</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-sm-4 col-md-4 col-lg-4">
                        <div class="">
                            <div class="dark-area clearfix">
                                <div class="c100 p88 green">
                                    <span>88%</span>
                                    <div class="slice">
                                        <div class="bar"></div>
