            </div>
        </div>


        <div id="testimonial">
                <div class="containers">
                    <div class="testimonialrow">
                        <div id="testimonial-slide" class="owl-carousel owl-theme testimonial-slide">                           
                            <div class="col-lg-4">
                                <div class="item">
                                    <div class="testimonial-quote-item">
                                        <img alt='Lori H' src='~/Content/Images/avatars.png' class='avatar avatar-80 photo' height='80' width='80' />
                                        <span class="quote-text">
                                            It was so quick and easy to sort out my flyer printing and delivery I thought it was a mistake. Such an efficient site that takes care of everything I needed. Will be using again. Thank you SG Fast Flyers.
                                        </span>
                                        <span class="quotes-author">– Lori H - Brisbane  </span>
                                    </div><!--/ Item end -->
                                </div>
                            </div>
                               
                            <div class="col-lg-4">
                                <div class="item">
                                    <div class="testimonial-quote-item">
                                        <img alt='Jane S' src='~/Content/Images/avatars.png' class='avatar avatar-80 photo' height='80' width='80' /><span class="quote-text">
                                            Even though the website was easy to use, I had some questions that I needed answered before I was able to go ahead. Adam and the team were quick and easy to deal with and had me sorted out in no time. Thanks Adam.
                                        </span>
                                        <span class="quotes-author">– Jane S – Rockhampton </span>
                                    </div><!--/ Item end -->
                                </div>
                            </div>


                                <div class="item">
                                    <div class="testimonial-quote-item">
                                        <img alt='Scotty' src='~/Content/Images/avatars.png' class='avatar avatar-80 photo' height='80' width='80' /><span class="quote-text">
                                            I knew exactly how many flyers I wanted delivered and printed, where they were going and when, so using www.sgfastflyers.com.au was a really pleasant experience. It has saved me about an hour a week. Great stuff.
                                        </span>
                                        <span class="quotes-author"> – Scotty – Geelong </span>
                                    </div>
                                </div><!--/ Item end -->


                                <div class="item">
                                    <div class="testimonial-quote-item">
                                        <img alt='Terry D' src='~/Content/Images/avatars.png' class='avatar avatar-80 photo' height='80' width='80' /><span class="quote-text">
                                            Great site, easy to use. Quick and efficient.
                                        </span>
                                        <span class="quotes-author"> – Terry D - Sydney </span>
                                    </div>
